{"tid":978564,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲女人比男人更加父權","createTime":"2019-01-12T04:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T04:33:08.000Z","uid":115189,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fc7cb1f6f06b32185bbbbb0a8b2f10c55b496106","tid":978564,"uid":115189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T04:28:57.000Z","msg":"成日都見香港啲女人好鐘意大大聲，當眾侮辱男人<br />\n<br />\n相反我從來未見過男人咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「你明唔明啊？」「咁係咪你錯啊？」「你知唔知我講乜啊？」<br />\n<br />\n大大聲慌死街上面聽唔到，唔畀個男嘅駁嘴，好似成個女皇帝咁，要落盡對方面，公開處刑咁<br />\n<br />\n個男嘅就覺得好肉酸，想息事寧人快啲走咁，但係你愈係尷尬冇面，佢就愈興奮，打蛇隨棍上，愈鬧愈大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5863529d1691faa674c295a83edb56a3e16ba288","tid":978564,"uid":82291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T04:31:16.000Z","msg":"你又知俾人鬧個個無做錯?"},{"pid":"d022cef91771a9c64c68f78daeecfadbac868a29","tid":978564,"uid":1425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T04:31:27.000Z","msg":"個男嘅太廢"},{"pid":"1fc470058107aad179cedd59806c645270d69bf2","tid":978564,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T04:33:00.000Z","msg":"班賤男人自己攞嚟"},{"pid":"514db4dc8f99c8188d5e6b50fe31356f524b2e83","tid":978564,"uid":115189,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5863529d1691faa674c295a83edb56a3e16ba288","tid":978564,"uid":82291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T04:31:16.000Z","msg":"你又知俾人鬧個個無做錯?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T04:33:08.000Z","msg":"咁錯咗都唔使咁掛，有冇見過女人做錯嘢咁樣畀個男人公開侮辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「你係咪錯啊？認錯啦」咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}